  "description": "The Department for Transport's measures to reduce energy consumption and costs, and carbon emissions",
  "details": {
    "body": "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Department publishes, in real-time, the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://webview2.ecodriver.net/dft/\">energy used in its headquarters building</a>. We also make our <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://data.gov.uk/dataset/dft-energy-use\" title=\"DFT energy use data\">energy use data</a> available in a format that can be reused.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"more-efficient-building\">More efficient building</h3>\n\n<p>To make our headquarters in London more efficient, we:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>are installing more energy-efficient lighting</li>\n  <li>have installed pulse meters on our electric and gas meters so we can identify and fix wastage</li>\n  <li>have switched off all unnecessary lighting in reception areas</li>\n  <li>have installed timers on all hot water heaters in tea-points so that theyâ€™re not on in the evenings or at weekends</li>\n  <li>have switched off and isolated all heaters in stairwells</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>We are currently assessing the CO2 benefits of the above measures.</p>\n\n<section class=\"attachment embedded\" id=\"attachment_1615191\">\n  <div class=\"attachment-thumb\">\n      <a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"thumbnail\" href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/533916/dft-display-energy-certificate.pdf\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/533916/thumbnail_dft-display-energy-certificate.pdf.png\"></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"attachment-details\">\n    <h2 class=\"title\"><a aria-describedby=\"attachment-1615191-accessibility-help\" href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/533916/dft-display-energy-certificate.pdf\"><abbr title=\"Department for Transport\">DfT</abbr> Display Energy Certificate</a></h2>\n    <p class=\"metadata\">\n        <span class=\"type\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"file-size\">299KB</span>, <span class=\"page-length\">1 page</span>\n    </p>\n\n\n      <div data-module=\"toggle\" class=\"accessibility-warning\" id=\"attachment-1615191-accessibility-help\">\n        <h2>This file may not be suitable for users of assistive technology.\n          <a class=\"toggler\" href=\"#attachment-1615191-accessibility-request\" data-controls=\"attachment-1615191-accessibility-request\" data-expanded=\"false\">Request an accessible format.</a>\n        </h2>\n        <p id=\"attachment-1615191-accessibility-request\" class=\"js-hidden\">\n          If you use assistive technology (such as a screen reader) and need a\nversion of this document in a more accessible format, please email <a href=\"mailto:webmasterdft@dft.gsi.gov.uk?body=Details%20of%20document%20required%3A%0A%0A%20%20Title%3A%20DfT%20Display%20Energy%20Certificate%0A%20%20Original%20format%3A%20pdf%0A%0APlease%20tell%20us%3A%0A%0A%20%201.%20What%20makes%20this%20format%20unsuitable%20for%20you%3F%0A%20%202.%20What%20format%20you%20would%20prefer%3F%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20&amp;subject=Request%20for%20%27DfT%20Display%20Energy%20Certificate%27%20in%20an%20alternative%20format\">webmasterdft@dft.gsi.gov.uk</a>.\nPlease tell us what format you need. It will help us if you say what assistive technology you use.\n\n        </p>\n      </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<h3 id=\"staff-behaviour-change\">Staff behaviour change</h3>\n\n<p>We also provide our staff with regular reminders and tips on how to save energy in the office, such as:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>turning off monitors when away from the desk</li>\n  <li>greater use of video or telephone conferencing</li>\n  <li>using the stairs instead of the lift</li>\n  <li>displaying weekly energy use on news screens in the department</li>\n</ul>\n\n</div>",
